    Interface Description
    EnterTileEffect
    Implement this interface when a figure entering the tile should trigger an effect/action.

    Class Description
    BuildableTile
    The abstract class BuildableTile may be inherited to define a certain Tile to be buildable.
    ConnectedPositions  
    GoalTile
    A goalTile used for creating goals for units to reach
    PathTile
    A PathTile used to represent all tiles that are walkable for units in the game
    StartTile
    A start tile used for creating starting areas for units
    TeleportTile  
    Tile
    The abstract parent class for tiles that all tiles have to extend.
    WallTile
    WallTiles are used to represent the end points of all levels.
    VoidTile
    A void tile used representing areas where towers are allowed to be build.
